ion of using mushrooms to dye fabrics.  Each color in a mushroom theme was pulled from a photograph included in the site from the given group.  The colors attempt to express the characteristic colors of the group.  In a few cases, the [:images] were adjusted using an automatic color balance operation in order to get a more characteristic color.\n\nThe following links describe each of the available themes including links to the [:images] the colors were extracted from:','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184925,1,746783232,'color_themes_title','Color Themes','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184926,1,746783232,'email_tracking_enabled_only_for','Enabled only for [name] -- contained taxa not yet supported for [rank].','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184927,1,746783232,'email_tracking_help','If you enable tracking then a note will be sent to the email address you have provided whenever this name is applied to an [:observation].  A link to this page will be given in each tracking email.  You can save your mailing address for collections in \"your profile\":/account/profile.','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184928,1,746783232,'email_tracking_no_longer_tracking','No longer tracking [name].','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184929,1,746783232,'email_tracking_note','Template for notifying an observer','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184930,1,746783232,'email_tracking_note_help','Provide a note template that will be sent as an email or shown to the observer when this name is applied to an [:observation].  If you leave it blank, then the observer will not be notified.','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184931,1,746783232,'email_tracking_note_template','Dear :observer,\n\nI am currently doing research related to [species_name].\n\nIf possible, please make a dried specimen of any of the mushrooms described in :observation and send them to:\n\n[mailing_address]\n\nThanks,\n\n[users_name]','2022-01-17 01:05:38',6209198),(1047184932,1,746783232,'email_tracking_n