erver/turn_javascript_on.  If you are tired of seeing the \"We Don\'t Recognize Your Browser\" tab at the top of every page, please \"click here to turn javascript off\":/observer/turn_javascript_off.  (Login and go to preferences to re-enable auto-detection.)','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185013,1,746783232,'no_browser_title','We Don\'t Recognize Your Browser','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185014,1,746783232,'no_email_how_to_reenable','Go to your \"Preferences\":/account/prefs page to re-enable this feature.','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185015,1,746783232,'no_email_some_maybe_queued','Note: For the next few minutes you may continue to receive emails that have already been queued.','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185016,1,746783232,'no_email_comments_owner_note','You will no longer receive email notifications when other [:users] of the [:app_title] website post [:comments] about your [:observations], names, etc.','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185017,1,746783232,'no_email_comments_response_note','You will no longer receive email notifications when other [:users] of the [:app_title] website post responses to your [:comments].','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185018,1,746783232,'no_email_comments_all_note','You will no longer receive email notifications of all [:comments].','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185019,1,746783232,'no_email_observations_consensus_note','You will no longer receive email notifications when the names of your [:observations] change.','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185020,1,746783232,'no_email_observations_naming_note','You will no longer receive email notifications when other [:users] of the [:app_title] website propose names for your [:observations].','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185021,1,746783232,'no_email_observations_all_note','You will no longer receive email notifications whenenver [:observations] change.','2022-01-17 01:05:39',6209198),(1047185022,1,746783232,'no_email_names_admin_note','